txt.en: Gladden gloomwaters can be found along the river Gladden.\n\nYou should defeat Gladden gloomwaters.
You have defeated many gloomwaters along the river Gladden, making the Vales of Anduin safer.
A strange darkness has come to the Vales of Anduin. Vile gloomwaters move along the river Gladden. These creatures should be defeated if the Vales are to remain safe.
Gloomwaters move along the river Gladden.
